# Monitoring and Logging Rules
tags: ["heartbeat", "summary", "monitoring"]
appliesTo: ["Ghost", "GPT", "CursorAgent"]
enforce: true
priority: high

## Rules

- `.clock-status.md` must update every 2 minutes.
- If heartbeat fails, execution must halt and GPT notified.
- All runtime logs must be saved to `/summaries/_heartbeat/`.
- Phase cannot be marked complete without diff, summary, and validator match.